model.name: Silhouette Sandal
model.disambiguatingDescription: This reinterpretation of the Silhouette sandal combines calf leather with Monogram canvas. The front strap is decorated with Monogram-Flower perforations, which are lined with metallic gold leather. This refined design is complemented by a Monogram Flower-shaped heel, while the ankle strap is fastened with an engraved, gold-tone buckle.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Gold
  • Perforated Monogram canvas and calf leather
  • Leather outsole
  • 8 cm / 3.1-inch heel
  • Monogram Flower-shaped heel
  • Louis Vuitton-engraved buckle
  • Made in Italy
